data.description: Plenty of space and equity available in this 4 bedroom house near the high school and the square. This is move in ready with the opportunity to put in sweat equity as similar homes updated in the area have sold for much more. There are 3 good sized bedrooms upstairs with a bathroom attached to two of them and a large walk-in closet off the primary suite. Another bedroom and full bathroom on the main level with a full size laundry room off the main floor bathroom. Outside enjoy a large 2 car garage, large deck, and nice yard for entertaining.
